alluxio.client.file

Class FileSystemWorkerClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • alluxio.AbstractThriftClient<FileSystemWorkerClientService.Client>
      • alluxio.client.file.FileSystemWorkerClient
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable

    @ThreadSafe
public class FileSystemWorkerClient
extends AbstractThriftClient<FileSystemWorkerClientService.Client>
implements Closeable
    Client for talking to a file system worker server. It keeps sending keep alive messages to the worker server to preserve its state. Since FileSystemWorkerClientService is not thread safe, this class guarantees thread safety.

      • sessionHeartbeat

        public void sessionHeartbeat()
                      throws IOException,
                             InterruptedException
        Sends a session heartbeat to the worker. This renews the client's lease on resources such as temporary files.
        Throws:
        IOException - if an I/O error occurs
        InterruptedException - if the heartbeat is interrupted
